  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK689">
<l>viṭumāṟṟam vēntark kuraippāṉ vaṭumāṟṟam</l>
<l>vāycōrā vaṉka ṇavaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He alone is fit to communicate (his sovereign's) reply, who possesses the firmness not to utter even inadvertently what may reflect discredit (on the latter).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
